machinevision (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Lightweight package without bundled Python dependencies
  * Uses system Python instead of virtualenv
  * Automatic dependency checking during installation
  * Package size: 74 KB (vs 58 MB with bundled deps)
  * Requires pre-installed Python dependencies on target system

 -- Machine Vision Team <support@example.com>  Fri, 08 Nov 2025 20:30:00 +0000
